  "texts": [
    "10 Clarivate identified 6,400 HCRs for the 2020 list in the WoS: 3,900 HCRs entered the list via the fieldspecific calculations, and 2,500 via the cross-field calculations.",
    "The reason for the higher author numbers identified in this study (compared to Clarivate) may be the larger number of publications in Scopus than in the WoS.",
    "The reason for the higher share of cross-field entries probably lies in the fact that Clarivate assigns each journal exactly to one field.",
    "We employed fractional assignments to each of the 35 FOS (see footnote 4).",
    "8 Our analyses build on the methods published in 2021."
  ]
}